texts.en:
This small loan is being requested by four borrowers, led by Mrs. Lim V., 24.  Lim and her husband are carrying workers for a busy fish market, working hard to earn money in order to feed their two children, both of whom are studying. To earn extra income, Lim is requesting her first loan as capital to begin selling a few grocery items from her home. <p>

The other three borrowers are:
K., who is looking for a loan to add to her savings to buy a motorbike for riding purposes;
R., who will be using this loan to repair and decorate her house;
P., a seller of cooking supplies, who is requesting a loan to buy more items to sell.
